  "detailed_description": "Collect all the abilities of Limos' Lair inhabitants and free the Lair of its curse. Challenging puzzles, enemies, and traps will be awaiting you on your path, but don't be afraid and follow a mysterious orb of light that will guide you through your journey.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GRAPPLE HOOK MECHANICS</h2>Use your tongue as a grappling hook or a weapon to navigate your path.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414500/extras/0421cd17f19b949507517ee87b80f846.poster.avif?t=1724952008\" width=640 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414500/extras/0421cd17f19b949507517ee87b80f846.webm?t=1724952008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414500/extras/0421cd17f19b949507517ee87b80f846.mp4?t=1724952008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414500/extras/ff2f88ba9ed3ecfdb24385cfdd00ea72.poster.avif?t=1724952008\" width=640 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414500/extras/ff2f88ba9ed3ecfdb24385cfdd00ea72.webm?t=1724952008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414500/extras/ff2f88ba9ed3ecfdb24385cfdd00ea72.mp4?t=1724952008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414500/extras/f405d2368ab6f3abca12c4a175bcd7bd.poster.avif?t=1724952008\" width=640 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414500/extras/f405d2368ab6f3abca12c4a175bcd7bd.webm?t=1724952008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414500/extras/f405d2368ab6f3abca12c4a175bcd7bd.mp4?t=1724952008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >POWERS</h2>Consume your enemies to steal their abilities.<br>Watch your enemies to find out what special powers they possess.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414500/extras/3ab9c2103889fdad6515fa9eaa41ab7b.poster.avif?t=1724952008\" width=640 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414500/extras/3ab9c2103889fdad6515fa9eaa41ab7b.webm?t=1724952008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414500/extras/3ab9c2103889fdad6515fa9eaa41ab7b.mp4?t=1724952008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ITEMS</h2>Find useful items on your journey.<br>Some of them will help you fight enemies and some will allow you to access previously unavailable areas.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414500/extras/a998443885d72c18841e13ac72eac0bf.avif?t=1724952008\" width=602 height=197 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OPEN WORLD</h2>You can explore new areas in any order you like.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414500/extras/b31bbe1dc00eb7cba0d96367a6c88185.avif?t=1724952008\" width=640 height=160 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414500/extras/ff1f4532ad9b0677e5f2c73e0578b7a3.avif?t=1724952008\" width=640 height=160 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414500/extras/8d94f5ee76e871610d63e4658a5f12ae.avif?t=1724952008\" width=640 height=160 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414500/extras/21c0c22ff80b53726387f4053a7ca9b6.avif?t=1724952008\" width=640 height=160 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414500/extras/4950c62b9aaf8c479e56add3823ff581.avif?t=1724952008\" width=640 height=160 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Consume enemies to gain their abilities.<br></li><li> Use your frog-like tongue as a grappling hook or as a weapon.<br></li><li> Explore the world, unlock new paths and solve puzzles by using different acquired powers.<br></li><li> Find secrets and complete challenges.</li></ul>",
